deepdep

Acquire and Visualise Deep Dependiences of R packages.

Installation

To install the package, use the following code:

devtools::install_github("DominikRafacz/deepdep")

This package was made during 1120-DS000-ISP-0500Advanced Programming in R course at Warsaw University of Technology.
